        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Welcome to FeedHope!</h2>
            <p>FeedHope is a community-driven organization dedicated to combating hunger and reducing food waste. Founded on the principles of compassion and sustainability, we believe in a world where no one has to go to bed hungry. Our primary mission is to provide nutritious food to those in need and to promote sustainable practices to minimize food waste.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>Our mission at FeedHope is twofold:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Alleviate Hunger:</strong> We aim to provide nutritious food to those who are food-insecure through effective and equitable distribution systems.</li>
                <li><strong>Reduce Food Waste:</strong> We strive to minimize food waste by creating sustainable solutions that repurpose surplus food for those in need.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>Our vision is a world where every person has reliable access to healthy food, and food waste is a thing of the past. We see a future where communities come together to support one another, ensuring that no food goes to waste and no person goes hungry.</p>
